<p>Dear Students,</p>
<p><br>
</p>
<p>Tomsk Polytechnic University is a National Research university which pla=
ces special emphasis on advanced engineering education, creation of resourc=
e-efficient technologies, internationalization and integration of research =
and academic activities.<br>
<br>
TPU was founded in 1896 and it is the second in ranking of the Russian Mini=
stry of Education and Science.TPU offers a number of degree programs mostly=
 in Russian and partly in English language. You can find information about =
TPU at
<a href=3D"http://tpu.ru/en">http://tpu.ru/en</a></p>
<p><br>
</p>
<strong style=3D"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);"><span style=3D"backgr=
ound-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">The Contest &quot;Your First Success&quot; i=
s aimed to provide 10 State academic Scholarships of Russia exclusively for=
 education at TPU Master Degree Programs in English.</span></strong>
<p><strong style=3D"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);"><span style=3D"bac=
kground-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">Tomsk Polytechnic University proposes 2 p=
rograms to IITM students:</span></strong></p>
<p><strong style=3D"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);"><span style=3D"bac=
kground-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">1. &quot;Biomedical Sciences and Engineer=
ing&quot; (the program is about all forms of Medical Tomography), developed=
 in cooperation with Siberian State Medical University</span></strong></p>
<p><strong style=3D"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);"><span style=3D"bac=
kground-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">2. &quot;Nuclear Power Installation Opera=
tion&quot; (the program is about Nuclear Reactor Operation),&nbsp;developed=
 in cooperation with Rosatom State Corporation</span></strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong style=3D"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);"><span style=3D"bac=
kground-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">All tests will include 30 questions: 10 q=
uestions in Math, 10 questions in Physics, and 10 questions in specific fie=
ld of particular program (Electronics
 for the first program and Nuclear Physics for the second program).</span><=
/strong></p>
<p><strong style=3D"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);"><span style=3D"bac=
kground-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">The &nbsp;maximum time for Contest is 50 =
min. (&#43;10 min. for introduction).</span></strong></p>
<strong style=3D"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);"><span style=3D"backgr=
ound-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">The scholarships will be granted on comperta=
tive base.</span></strong>
<p><br>
</p>
<p><strong style=3D"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(255, =
0, 0);">Venue: MRC</span></strong></p>
<p><strong style=3D"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(255, =
0, 0);">Date : March 29th</span></strong></p>
<p><strong style=3D"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(255, =
0, 0);">Time: 5.00 p.m. - 6.00 p.m.</span></strong><br style=3D"color: rgb(=
255, 0, 0);">
<strong style=3D"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"></strong></p>
<p><br>
</p>
<p><br>
As a development of Indo- Russian Friendship in the field of education &amp=
; research,&nbsp;The Committee of TPU decided to provide special TPU contes=
t &quot;Your first success&quot; for state academic scholarships for TPU Ma=
ster Degree programs in English,</p>
<p>1. State Academic Scholarship was confirms for 10 Indian students to stu=
dy at TPU at 5 Master Degree Programs in&nbsp;</p>
<p>English&nbsp;<a href=3D"http://iie.tpu.ru/en/3_programs_english_master.p=
hp">http://iie.tpu.ru/en/3_programs_english_master.php</a><a href=3D"http:/=
/iie.tpu.ru/en/3_programs_english_master.php">http://iie.tpu.ru/en/3_progra=
ms_english_master.php</a>&nbsp;(except &nbsp;Petroleum
 Engineering). PhD programs are also available, but only for study in Russi=
an medium with Pr-university course of Russian</p>
<p>2. The Contest will be organized by Tomsk Polytechnic University under t=
he direct guidance of Institute of International education. 4 TPU departmen=
ts(Institutes) were involved in preparing of the Contest (Institute of High=
 Technology Physics,&nbsp;Institute of
 Cybernetics,&nbsp;Institute of Physics and Technology,Institute of Non-Des=
tructive Testing)&nbsp;
</p>
<p><br>
</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>IITM students are also very welcome to participate in the international =
Contest &quot;it's time to study in Russia&quot; launched by Russian univer=
sities in 2013.</p>
<p>TPU is coordinator of this Contest in India. 5 Scholarships for Master D=
egree program &quot;Computer Science&quot; (in Russian) will be available (=
one year of Pre-university &nbsp;course will be included for free). The Con=
test will be organized in RCSC Chennai in 4-5 April.&nbsp;</p>
<p><br>
</p>
<p>With regards</p>
<p>Kavitha<br>
